# Real Data Sample Requirements

Some implementation details cannot be finalized until real data is inspected.

This file defines what samples are needed.

---

## Aimlabs Sample Needed

Need one redacted sample from Aimlabs.

Useful sources:
- local task data
- JSON export
- CSV export
- any file Aimlabs stores recent results in

We need to inspect:

```text
scenario/task name
score
date/time
accuracy
duration
mode/task ID if available
playlist/benchmark name if available
extra metrics
file update behavior
folder structure
```

Redact:
- username
- account ID
- private paths if desired

Keep:
- field names
- sample values
- structure

