## Benchmark Source Samples Needed

Need source examples for:

```text
Voltaic thresholds
Viscose thresholds
one generic community sheet if available
```

Acceptable formats:
- public Google Sheet CSV
- exported CSV
- copied threshold table
- GitHub JSON/CSV
- official docs page manually converted later

Need metadata:
- source name
- source URL if public
- official/community/unknown
- version/date
- notes about permission/trust

---

## Development Without Real Samples

If samples are missing, Codex should:

- build interfaces
- build fixture importers
- build validators
- build engine
- avoid claiming real parser completeness

Do not guess real file formats.

---

## Sample Fixture Policy

Synthetic fixtures should be clearly marked:

```text
tests/fixtures/synthetic/
```

Real redacted fixtures should be marked:

```text
tests/fixtures/redacted/
```

Do not commit private personal data.
